engine
Class Instrument

java.lang.Object
  engine.Instrument
Direct Known Subclasses:
DirectedInstrument, UndirectedInstrument
public abstract class Instrument
extends java.lang.Object

The Instrument class stores a single instrument within an orchestra or band. Instruments are transient objects and exist only for calculations for the distortion with seats in mind.

Author:
Jonathan Sun
